articles.author: Ellen Francis
articles.title: Corruption probe close to Zelensky stokes E.U. unease over Ukraine aid - The Washington Post
articles.description: A scandal, involving kickbacks at Ukraine’s state nuclear power company, has revived concerns about European money being siphoned off by graft instead of helping fight Russia.
